<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2617615>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–9. Aedeagi in ventral view of: (7) S. gracilis (Hornos, Spain); (8) Lectotype of S. tenuipes (Zaccar, Algeria); (9) S. tenuipes (Djurdjura, Algeria)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2617615/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2617619>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–28. Apex of the parameres of: (13) Speonemadus orchesioides (Ammi-Moussa, Algeria); (14) holotype of S. brusteli sp. n. (Talembote, Morocco); (15) S. gracilis (Hornos, Spain); (16) S. tenuipes (Ifri Semedane, Algeria); (17) S. vandalitiae (Villanúa, Spain); (18) S. pulchellus (Ficuzza, Sicily); (19) holotype of S. algarvensis (Gruta do Vale Telheiro, Portugal); (20) S. angusticollis (Rute, Spain); (21) S. bolivari (Ardales, Spain); (22) S. breuili (Motillas, Spain); (23) S. escalerai (Jumilla, Spain); (24) S. transversostriatus (La Bastida, Spain); (25) S. clathratus (Linarejos, Spain); (26) S. maroccanus (Taza, Morocco); (27) holotype of S. comasi sp. n. (Tagelft, Morocco); (28) Anemadus hajeki (Yunnan, China)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2617619/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2617621>
    dc:description "FIGURE 29. Lectotype of Choleva gracilis (scale bar: specimen, 2 mm; aedeagus, 0.6 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2617621/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2617617>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10–11. Aedeagi in ventral view of: (10) S. vandalitiae (Villanúa, Spain); (11) S. pulchellus (Ficuzza, Sicily)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2617617/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2617641>
    dc:description "FIGURE 39. Distribution maps of: (39) S. gracilis, S. vandalitiae. See Appendix for detailed locality data." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2617641/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

